name: MetricStructuredName
description:
Identifies a metric, by describing the source which generated the metric.

params.name: data

params.name: data.origin
params.description: Origin (namespace) of metric name. May be blank for user-define metrics; will be "dataflow" for metrics defined by the Dataflow service or SDK.

params.name: data.context
params.description: Zero or more labeled fields which identify the part of the job this metric is associated with, such as the name of a step or collection.
